I already read that file. The RescueApiResponse is:
```typescript
export interface RescueApiResponse {
  status?: { message: string };
  data?: { status?: string };
}
```

And the original ResgateResponse is:
```typescript
interface ResgateResponse {
  status: { message: string };
  data?: { status: string };
}
```

So after the API unwraps `response.data`:
